{"tid":2401747,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣電影, 大陸電影 入圍奧斯卡初選15強","createTime":"2021-02-10T03:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T07:11:32.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"17f7dd194a0755675fc37bbd0b6e8d4e6f663cd9","tid":2401747,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"「少年的你」係大陸電影,&nbsp;但香港電影製片家協會決定推薦「少年的你」代表香港角逐奧斯卡金像獎,&nbsp;放棄真香港本土電影「幻愛」.&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102105001.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202102105001.aspx&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQqy4iG8TIfC1p449sO1N5Ck%3D&h=a141ba9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102105001.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者林宏翰洛杉磯9日專電）台灣電影「陽光普照」1月底進入角逐奧斯卡最佳國際影片的候選名單，今天再傳好消息，經首輪投票之後，名列15部初選名單影片，奪獎路上往前邁進一步。<br />\n.....<br />\n 經過首輪投票，「陽光普照」的競爭對手今天縮小範圍，將與其他14部各國電影進入下一輪投票，爭取進入3月15日公布的正式入圍名單。第93屆頒獎典禮將在4月25日舉辦。<br />\n<br />\n15部候選的國際影片裡，「陽光普照」、香港電影「少年的你」、伊朗電影「太陽之子」（暫譯）（SunChildren）是3部來自亞洲的作品。"},{"pid":"fb4a2da66e8ff501b9e2c9ed5a3b5bf2dd2d5e20","tid":2401747,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:32:51.000Z","msg":"都恭喜「陽光普照」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd2c1822a6e314709c0bcee13535ffd6eb9c43f","tid":2401747,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T07:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}